query:
INSERT INTO usage (
            api_key_id, model_id, user_id,
            total_input_tokens, total_output_tokens
        )
        SELECT
            ak.api_key_id, m.model_id, ak.user_id,
            $3, $4
        FROM
            (
                SELECT api_key_id, user_id
                FROM api_keys
                WHERE api_key = $1
            ) ak,
            (
                SELECT model_id
                FROM models
                WHERE model_name = $2
            ) m
